Now you have a simple blog app that uses the JSONPlaceholder API to fetch data and statically generates pages for all the blog posts. This example demonstrates how to use `generateStaticParams` and `generateMetadata` functions in Next.js 13 with TypeScript to fetch and display data from an external API.
